===Pokémon Adventures===
{{main|Pearl (Adventures)}}
In [[Pokémon Adventures]], Barry has a counterpart named {{adv|Pearl}}. Together with his friend {{adv|Diamond}}, they form an aspiring {{wp|manzai}} comedy duo. Pearl also has the talent of being able to predict what [[move]] a Pokémon is going to use simply by observing its body language.
